OL,3,CAnti-PSNI posters spotted in Lurgan
OL,4,Cjust days after recruitment drive
OL,5,Cfinished
OL,7,FA number of anti-PSNI posters have
OL,8,Fbeen spotted in Lurgan, just days
OL,9,Fafter the force's latest recruitment
OL,10,Fcampaign came to an end.
OL,12,FThey were put up by a socialist
OL,13,Frepublican group who say they are not
OL,14,Ftrying to intimidate potential
OL,15,Frecruits but instead point out their
OL,16,Fown opinion of the PSNI.
OL,18,FHowever, Carla Lockhart, a DUP MP,
OL,19,Fsaid the intention was "clearly to
OL,20,Fintimidate and create a real chilling
OL,21,Feffect within the local community".
