OL,7,FSimilarly, SLDP MLA Mark Durkan said
OL,8,Fhis party was "unequivocal in its
OL,9,Fcondemnation of any poster that is
OL,10,Fdesigned to attack or intimidate or
OL,11,Faggravate".
OL,13,FAll of this comes as a recent PSNI
OL,14,Frecruitment drive saw less than 30% of
OL,15,Fthe 4,822 applicants coming from a
OL,16,FCatholic background.
