OL,7,FReacting to the figures, Liam Kelly
OL,8,Fwho is Chair of the Police Federation
OL,9,Ffor Northern Ireland (PFNI), said
OL,10,Fthere is still some way to go to
OL,11,Fremoving the obstacles, real or
OL,12,Fperceived, that many with a Catholic
OL,13,Fbackground feel are in place when they
OL,14,Fconsider applying for the police.
OL,16,FMr Kelly said: "I welcome this level
OL,17,Fof response. It shows there is
OL,18,Fextensive interest in a police career
OL,19,Fwhile also pointing to work that is
OL,20,Fcontinuing to attract increased
OL,21,Fnumbers from a Catholic background.
