OL,7,F"The outreach work that was done was
OL,8,Fand remains extensive. The plain and
OL,9,Fsimple truth is that despite best
OL,10,Fefforts, Catholics are still put off
OL,11,Fapplying to become student officers
OL,12,Ffor a number of reasons but especially
OL,13,Fbecause of threat levels posed by
OL,14,Fdissident republicans."
OL,16,FThe Deputy Chief Constable of the
OL,17,FPSNI, Bobby Singleton, has welcomed
OL,18,Fthe announcement that nearly 5,000
