OL,7,FHe said: "We were conscious that we
OL,8,Fwould be operating in very competitive
OL,9,Fjob market, with the Northern Ireland
OL,10,Funemployment rate at a record low of
OL,11,Fjust 1.9%. A recent report by the
OL,12,FUlster University's Economic Policy
OL,13,FCentre also highlighted a shortage of
OL,14,F5,440 workers a year, resulting in an
OL,15,Fundersupply of available workers
OL,16,Facross almost all sectors and
OL,17,Findustries.
